    <refpurpose>ganeti remote API daemon</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <cmdsynopsis>
      <command>&dhpackage; </command>

    </cmdsynopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>
  <refsect1>
    <title>DESCRIPTION</title>

    <para>
      <command>&dhpackage;</command> is the daemon providing a remote API for
      Ganeti clusters.
    </para>

    <para>
      It is automatically started on the master node if enabled at build time.
      Encryption via SSL can be enabled by using command line parameters.
    </para>

    <para>
      Take a look at the <emphasis>Ganeti remote API</emphasis> documentation
      for further information.
    </para>

    <para>
      Requests are logged to
      <filename>@LOCALSTATEDIR@/log/ganeti/rapi-access.log</filename> in a
      format similar to Apache's Common Log Format. The timestamp is always in
      the UTC timezone.
    </para>

  </refsect1>

  &footer;

</refentry>

